(self.webpackChunkfun_doc=self.webpackChunkfun_doc||[]).push([[7764],{7152:(e,a,r)=>{"use strict";r.r(a),r.d(a,{data:()=>s});const s={key:"v-6838250e",path:"/android/AndroidStudio%E5%8F%8Agradle%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%B1%87%E6%80%BB.html",title:"问题汇总",lang:"zh-CN",frontmatter:{},excerpt:"",headers:[{level:2,title:"1. gradle报错",slug:"_1-gradle报错",children:[]}],filePathRelative:"android/AndroidStudio及gradle问题汇总.md",git:{updatedTime:162452411e4,contributors:[{name:"caifang",email:"cooldish1245@163.com",commits:1}]}}},2695:(e,a,r)=>{"use strict";r.r(a),r.d(a,{default:()=>l});const s=(0,r(6252).uE)('<h1 id="问题汇总"><a class="header-anchor" href="#问题汇总">#</a> 问题汇总</h1><h2 id="_1-gradle报错"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_1-gradle报错">#</a> 1. gradle报错</h2><p>场景： 项目<code>build.gradle</code>中指定gradle版本：</p><div class="language-gradle ext-gradle line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-gradle"><code>    dependencies {\n        classpath &#39;com.android.tools.build:gradle:3.0.0&#39;\n    }\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br></div></div><p><code>gradle-wrapper.properties</code>中指定gradle插件版本:</p><div class="language-gradle ext-gradle line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-gradle"><code>distributionUrl=https\\://services.gradle.org/distributions/gradle-5.4.1-all.zip\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>报错：</p><div class="language-console ext-console line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-console"><code>Unable to find method &#39;org.gradle.api.tasks.compile.CompileOptions.setBootClasspath(Ljava/lang/String;)V&#39;.\nPossible causes for this unexpected error include:\nGradle&#39;s dependency cache may be corrupt (this sometimes occurs after a network connection timeout.)\nRe-download dependencies and sync project (requires network)\n...\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br></div></div><p>这一般是<code>gradle-wrapper.properties</code>中指定gradle插件版本和<code>build.gradle</code>中版本不兼容导致。 2者的版本不一定一致，但有的版本之间是不兼容的.</p><p>修改<code>gradle-wrapper.properties</code>中指定的版本为：</p><div class="language-gradle ext-gradle line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-gradle"><code>distributionUrl=https\\://services.gradle.org/distributions/gradle-4.1-all.zip\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>问题得以解决。</p><p>结论： <code>gradle-wrapper.properties</code>中指定的版本原则： 兼容项目中指定的gradle版本，兼容第三方包。</p><p>目前比较通用的：</p><div class="language-gradle ext-gradle line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-gradle"><code>distributionUrl=https\\://services.gradle.org/distributions/gradle-4.1-all.zip\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>目前较新的：(用于第三方包使用了新版gradle插件时，去兼容)</p><div class="language-gradle ext-gradle line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-gradle"><code>distributionUrl=https\\://services.gradle.org/distributions/gradle-5.4.1-all.zip\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div>',17),l={render:function(e,a){return s}}}}]);